{"tid":2447243,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想討論PT (Private tracker)","createTime":"2021-03-15T05:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T13:32:25.000Z","uid":31846,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1418767ebbe7adffa44c63825379aa32d51afe8d","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"唔知呢版啱唔啱,香港都好小人討論呢樣野,幾年前HKEPC都有人提下,近年幾乎完全無人討論<br />\n年半前買左NAS之後,搜下搜下就見到,當其時覺得係黑暗野,但在無野玩搵野玩之後便上左癮<br />\n有時根本唔係為左個D資源而係為個上載率!唔知呢度有無人玩PT,本人都係玩左無耐,大既得饅頭同埋(島)(都係捐番來既),細既就有學校同埋海膽,玩唔到咁多,無咁多HDD位!<br />\n<br />\n一齊討論下!(討論埋NAS既技術都可以)"},{"pid":"dfd9551f4fc714e7344dc071491149cf465e39b1","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnnZRpm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnnZRpm.png&h=6b87c311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30938f903af018779fa9e4cc884449aacf7db66e","tid":2447243,"uid":204194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"pt 通常有咩特別資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一般bt好似夠做?<br />\n<br />\n另外因為pt難入 咁係咪代表down得好慢? <br />\n定正正相反個個都做種去俾貢獻 所以好快<br />\n<br />\n加上應該唔多人有咁大容量去keep 4k bd個啲 要賺夠貢獻都要好耐"},{"pid":"7181667f8c924711b6f627bddd7722ff7df36365","tid":2447243,"uid":15403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"淨係得jpopsuki<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e47ba5f8b487b7e5856247c374cfdef3154f341","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30938f903af018779fa9e4cc884449aacf7db66e","tid":2447243,"uid":204194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"pt 通常有咩特別資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一般bt好似夠做?<br />\n<br />\n另外因為pt難入 咁係咪代表down得好慢? <br />\n定正正相反個個都做種去俾貢獻 所以好快<br />\n<br />\n加上應該唔多人有咁大容量去keep 4k bd個啲 要賺夠貢獻都要好耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"三大站基本滿速,因大部份人都搶上傳,<br />\n一般BT好多斷種,PT入面連D咸豐年前既野都仲可以下到仲好快<br />\n<br />\n玩親既識玩既一定會KEEP資源(見過有D人KEEP住幾千種)<br />\n,仲有D會租SEEDBOX去玩(為既都係想升級同埋搶上傳)"},{"pid":"a97a0f86da54af47ad4bce52d0632eda9a3321cc","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"至於你話有咩特別資源....如果大站既話,你講得出既都應該有,你講唔出都應該會有(遊戲,軟件,寫真,漫畫甜漫,古代電影電視劇,正式教學資源...連D九唔搭八你想唔到既野都竟然會有!)"},{"pid":"a768dcaefa7d634994c6b00cffae945892cbc36d","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4CyWoY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4CyWoY.png&h=561a2c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9tExsvD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9tExsvD.png&h=88df2aa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31b852da1086cb29589c5717ed8133b5f6e15947","tid":2447243,"uid":101554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"連登邊有人玩<br />\n個個Netflix bilibili porthub streaming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898636269f021d3cef070d53e973d6f437ec2660","tid":2447243,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"有冇新手入門<br />\n聽都未聽過, google緊"},{"pid":"0c427d1c5dcec9e7356662eb90bfa3c761018d5c","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"898636269f021d3cef070d53e973d6f437ec2660","tid":2447243,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"有冇新手入門<br />\n聽都未聽過, google緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"呢樣野其實都有十年歷史,可能就正如上面位師兄講,香港人興串流,<br />\n而且PT如果要認真玩既話,硬件門檻點都要有些小,再加上因為版權原因怕封殺做成封閉既小圈子,所以香港真係無太多人知同無乜人玩了.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfrDoxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfrDoxZ.png&h=3edfa13a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01125610aa6e0d89355a0491b2954c8db9a4b65c","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"898636269f021d3cef070d53e973d6f437ec2660","tid":2447243,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"有冇新手入門<br />\n聽都未聽過, google緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"香港根本無人討論,你要新手入門既資訊大部份都係大陸同台灣的<br />\n俾個初部概念,就係呢個圈有一規則,你要攞野就先要俾野出去<br />\n個系統會紀錄你俾左幾多,而你就相應可以拿番幾多,如果你拿既多過俾既,就會俾人踢出局!呢個就係PT既大概玩法!<br />\nBT既人就係下完就走<br />\nPT想生存就係死都唔走做種!"},{"pid":"a7bb0caadb9de4695aca3e6c97074bb27ac54fad","tid":2447243,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"太巴閉"},{"pid":"d7e5a9dd5aa9f63de70fdb18c675388dd1767d25","tid":2447243,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a97a0f86da54af47ad4bce52d0632eda9a3321cc","tid":2447243,"uid":31846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"至於你話有咩特別資源....如果大站既話,你講得出既都應該有,你講唔出都應該會有(遊戲,軟件,寫真,漫畫甜漫,古代電影電視劇,正式教學資源...連D九唔搭八你想唔到既野都竟然會有!)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"睇咗你啲圖 真係咩都有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好被動好難升level 冇人download就冇得升呢<br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打有幾多容量 for pt <br />\n我覺得冇十幾tb 都唔係好玩得起"},{"pid":"6bdd4de54536bd92ac7d12a2a5636a010e3cd418","tid":2447243,"uid":383055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"我淨係會down動畫果類其他都係在線資源解決，就淨係入u2（因為夠易入）,有想入Animebytes但係睇到佢入會既難度還是免了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df60e093633296dd7620ca545b613c678940cde9","tid":2447243,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bdd4de54536bd92ac7d12a2a5636a010e3cd418","tid":2447243,"uid":383055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"我淨係會down動畫果類其他都係在線資